    "title": "Learning Graphs: The Key to Intelligent Textbooks",
    "description": "A learning graph covering the data structures, standards, and workflows used to design, validate, visualize, and generate interactive intelligent textbooks \u2014 concept dependency graphs (CDGs), taxonomies, generative-AI concept enumeration, vis.js visualization, and the learning-science foundations that justify DAG-based instructional sequencing.",
